high_descs: Take a potato out of the fridge.
Bring the potato to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the potato to the green trash bin.
Put the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the trash bin.

high_descs: Move to the refrigerator to the left
Grab the piece of fruit from inside the refrigerator.
Move to the microwave to the left of the refrigerator
Microwave the fruit briefly and pick it back up
Move to the bin to the left of the stove
Put the fruit in the bin
anns.task_desc: Throw away the fruit you microwave from the refrigerator,

high_descs: take coconut off of top right shelf of refrigerator
go to counter with microwave to the left
place coconut in microwave to the left side of the plate
turn on microwave, remove coconut from microwave
turn around, go to green can on floor next to stove, place coconut in green can
anns.task_desc: Place microwaved coconut in green can
